node.text: VINCEY. The icon. The legend. The STAR. Honey, no one does it better. I love you so much and I’m so proud of you and your evolution. I am so excited for the world to be obsessed with you like I am. I love you. oh, and HAPPY BITCHIN BIRTHDAYYYY @vincerossi
